{"tid":2434422,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"曾偉雄：奴才執行黨安法跟足黨例 所謂濫捕只是情緒化的感覺","createTime":"2021-03-05T13:45:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T13:51:34.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3fec3b86e5303e3681ae641f6b3586623d9cd085","tid":2434422,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T13:45:03.000Z","msg":"曾偉雄：警方執行國安法跟足法例精神 唯部分人從感情層面覺濫捕<br />\n<br />\n在北京出席全國兩會的全國政協委員、警務處前處長曾偉雄認為，本港警方執行《港區國安法》時，有跟足法律目標、法治精神，亦有保障到人權，執法過程雖然嚴厲，但是根據法例行事。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，如果從感情層面，同情被補人士的人可能會覺得警方濫捕，但認為從執法角度，警方並無濫捕，強調確保國家安全是特區的責任，反問如果無警方嚴格執行《港區國安法》，如何履行有關責任。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2381783\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2381783&d=sOSR1epLEapJbLCvIyWedazbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=6c653db2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2381783</a>"},{"pid":"267cf5ff458faf83db3b7c5d287c5955d6020366","tid":2434422,"uid":105691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T13:46:24.000Z","msg":"好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef03662c388c76aa3f623c35fff91354f8e17954","tid":2434422,"uid":27605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T13:47:18.000Z","msg":"黑警同你講:我打份工架渣"},{"pid":"d234f7e68220c385836af3df01074b0e3efe9a72","tid":2434422,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T13:50:25.000Z","msg":"立惡法然後同人講依法辦事<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9834da700dc21bd53399fb55816b95e1d00e4bc1","tid":2434422,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T13:51:34.000Z","msg":"活嚮平衡時空嘅支那賤畜"}]}